Date: Sun, 14 Jul 2013 22:41:23 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0209/1072] ENGR00269945: ARM: imx: add CONFIG_GPIO_PCA953X
 into defconfig

git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_3.10.17_1.0.0_beta
commit 42b48d395d15a91004d4b82422cc1d527daf4181

CONFIG_GPIO_PCA953X enables driver support for MAX7310 which is used on
imx6qdl-sabreauto board for IO expanders.

Signed-off-by: Shawn Guo <shawn.guo@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Hongbo Zhong <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
index 748537d..cc58452 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
@@ -148,6 +148,7 @@ CONFIG_SPI=y
 CONFIG_SPI_IMX=y
 CONFIG_GPIO_SYSFS=y
 CONFIG_GPIO_MC9S08DZ60=y
+CONFIG_GPIO_PCA953X=y
 # CONFIG_HWMON is not set
 CONFIG_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_IMX2_WDT=y
